headline: Dynamis Power Solutions Awards Baker Hughes With Significant Order for Gas Turbine Technology to Support Mobile Power for Oil & Gas Applications
summary: HOUSTON, November 20, 2025--Dynamis Power Solutions, LLC (Dynamis), a leading mobile power generation packager in North America, and Baker Hughes, an energy technology company, announced Thursday a significant order, booked in the third quarter of 2025, for 25 aeroderivative gas turbines – including LM2500, LM6000 and LM9000 – totaling 1.3GW for mobile power generation across a wide range of oil & gas applications, including upstream, refining, and petrochemical.
